{"tid":372233,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"落車忘拉「手掣」　司機救車慘遭夾死","createTime":"2017-08-24T07:56:23.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-25T01:31:42.000Z","uid":20933,"like":35,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c38773dcaf1f3b8eef21e90b752dd92ca939e175","tid":372233,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T07:56:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170824/large/1503557964_a5bf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170824%2Flarge%2F1503557964_a5bf.jpg&h=02c3b023&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中午12時，九龍灣宏開道20號楊耀松第八工業大廈，63歲姓許男司機駕駛重型貨車，駛至停車場，他倒後車時，左車尾撞到其他車輛，他遂入「d波」向前，但無拉手掣，擬查看車尾撞毀情況，惟此時貨車繼續向前溜駛，司機發現疑欲跳上車停車，惟貨車溜前，直指泊在旁邊另一部貨車，司機慘被夾在兩車間重創，當場昏迷不醒，獲救後送院，惜經搶救後不治，警方正調查意外原因。<br />\n<br />\n工業傷亡權益會的社工已到醫院了解事件，並接觸到死者家屬，死者有兩名已成年女兒，該會將提供情緒輔導及其他適切協助。"},{"pid":"0f2c95ab7e89bf03952ce1938ec592ddf10c9c05","tid":372233,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T07:57:30.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170824&amp;guid=57121367&amp;category_guid=10829391&amp;category=instant\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170824%26guid%3D57121367%26category_guid%3D10829391%26category%3Dinstant&d=x2ap%2B2O%2Fy76MWOXZsG3IFwdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=5380dd19\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fissue%3D20170824%26guid%3D57121367%26category_guid%3D10829391%26category%3Dinstant&h=bc898ef0\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?issue=20170824&amp;guid=57121367&amp;category_guid=10829391&amp;category=instant</a>"},{"pid":"89bc5facff7118a5c3a65b2db1c26d465fd4162c","tid":372233,"uid":40422,"like":8,"dislike":51,"score":-43,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T07:59:08.000Z","msg":"想睇冇碼版"},{"pid":"5a54635518af188d45fafdb22ff196b3b79802db","tid"